{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"d722e829076a3f10e94aff36bee9e71d1409744678a431e0da899c47f2088c8f","slug":"meta-domain","location":"/essay/stdn/meta_domain.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"元标准：标准设计时无处安放的幽灵","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":2}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/essay/stdn/meta_domain.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/essay/stdn/meta_domain.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"meta_domain.md","url":"/meta_domain-07d13acb7ccc13f70a496b427411e9fd.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在设计标准时，总会遇到一些概念——它们不属于任何一个具体标准，但又反复出现在所有标准里。","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"CnME8KjU6x"}],"key":"KbIbGzVm9h"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"比如“时间”。事件记忆标准需要它，语义记忆标准也需要它，档案标准需要它，日志标准更需要它。你放在哪儿？每个标准都自己定义一遍？那将来肯定打架。单独抽出来？抽出来放哪儿？","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"SlnvCoDzdi"}],"key":"FNoCkf1WBo"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"再比如“类型”。事件有类型，记忆有类型，交付物也有类型。这个“类型”的概念本身，到底归谁管？","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"ld7PpYsnSA"}],"key":"TVnImedQgE"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"还有“状态”、“来源”、“版本”……这些幽灵一样的概念，飘在所有标准的上空，却找不到一个落脚的地方。","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"xd7RhhVj5E"}],"key":"homKr1Vw6f"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"元标准就是给这些幽灵准备的收容所。","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"cXAwlKpW5Z"}],"key":"vPXY5kqmzU"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"它不是用来定义具体业务规则的，而是专门收容那些**“不知道放哪里但又必须存在”**的概念。它把所有标准都会用到的基础概念统一捞出来，给它们一个家，定义清楚它们是什么、能干什么、和其他概念是什么关系。","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"lbt07nmeeY"}],"key":"O0z7roq8kx"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"从此以后，再设计新标准时，遇到“时间”这种幽灵，就不用纠结了——直接看元标准，那里已经有一个现成的“时间”概念，引用它就行。所有标准都用同一个“时间”，自然就对齐了。","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"key":"Rte3PyOPjQ"}],"key":"UEiDs0PTEF"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"元标准不是设计出来的，是","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"XMCvk4Hzry"},{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在设计的纠结中被迫长出来的","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"ADUl9RlE9X"}],"key":"NicDuKOYTX"},{"type":"text","value":"。发现概念没地方放，反复出现，无处安放——于是有了它。","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"axwRizPXGZ"}],"key":"HpVnlgSQay"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"它是标准的影子，是所有标准背后的那层元语言。","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"KBMZO9psCj"}],"key":"FfNvQk56Vs"}],"key":"q9T1vJkIkr"}],"key":"pECVTIGBoi"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}